Joystick input!
I picked up a Madcatz stick of some sort so I could play space shooters and 6DOF shooters.
Ever since then I've been thinking of hooking it up for game prototypes.
Well, this is the first step!

This was intended to be a 30 minute task, but took just over 60 minutes.

Requirements:

- gcc
- sdl2
- nemiver (for using the `debug' command)

Setup:

> cd /path/to/project/root
> source env/shell

Building:

> build

Running:

> run

Debugging:

> debug